274783233.name: Black & White—Legendary Treasures
274783233.description: Legends lost are recovered, buried treasures are found, and in the Pokémon TCG: Black & White—Legendary Treasures expansion, Pokémon as you've never seen them will dazzle you! Discover new Pokémon-EX, as well as the return of mighty champions. Find new Trainer cards to revolutionize your battle strategy! Command your forces and drive onward to victory! Locate the scattered jewels of the Radiant Collection! And, above all, hunt for the golden glimmers that signify an amazing find…
